Date: 2010-02-12

Fixed typo in manual

-------------------
Version: 0.12
Date: 2009-10-15

Added log fold-change transformation

-------------------
Version: 0.11
Date: 2009-07-06

Cleaned up the package vignette a little

-------------------
Version: 0.10
Date: 2009-07-06

Added specific namespace calls to nlme so that lme4 methods do not interfere.



